      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "12517-12583",
      "markText": "班廷他们的研发团队以1美元的价格把专利卖给了多伦多大学。班廷曾经说过，胰岛素不属于他们，而是属于全世界的，他们放弃了成为富翁的机会。",
      "totalCount": 1020,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018844&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=12517&rangeEnd=12583",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41432a60813ab6ddcg01417f?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=12517&rangeEnd=12583"
    },
